channel.title: Comments on: Tech Start-Up Evening in Sligo

item.title: By: Heather James
item.dc:creator: Heather James
item.description: At the Open Coffee group, we're working on an event for November, Northwest Connects, to showcase start-ups and businesses from the region. A learning and exchange event to some extent, speakers will share expertise and "war stories" from the likes of Johnathan Hill of Infacta/PollDaddy, and other businesses. The plan is shaping up fast. We'll have more info soon!
